{"tid":211085,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"前幾日拎左darksouls3既白金成就","createTime":"2017-04-21T11:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T07:46:50.000Z","uid":70429,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"883f05461a0b6eedbaaa95d476a4fe66e7bc415f","tid":211085,"uid":70429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"之後其他所有遊戲都唔想玩,<br />\n<br />\n好似放下心頭大石咁,<br />\n<br />\n連DS3個game本體都唔想再掂,<br />\n<br />\n你可能話仲有好多game個劇場好過佢,刺激過佢,難過佢,<br />\n<br />\n但我對於DS3好迷戀,<br />\n<br />\n成隻game好黑暗,陰沉,各種血腥,獵奇,嘔心,怪異元素.<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n<br />\n當你發現賊仔為左幫你偷野最尾死左係屋頂,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現帕奇雖然奸詐但會去救賊仔,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現希莉絲幫完你打雙王子之後自殺,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現極度好學既魔法師,最後係大書庫坐係度死,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現灰心撚最尾同你堂堂正正單挑,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現把口勁臭但其實內心好在乎修女既巨棒佬死係修女牢房度,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現黃指頭重生得太多次,最尾變成蟲,<br />\n<br />\n當你發現洋蔥哥打完巨人之後自殺左.<br />\n<br />\n當你發現一路上比鼓勵你,比路標你既安里要自己親手殺or變成遊魂...<br />\n<br />\n同埋,<br />\n<br />\n當你殺左爺爺,然後小畫家問爺爺幾時先會拎顏料比佢,而佢正正打算畫一幅溫暖既畫比爺爺住.<br />\n<br />\n成隻game就係咁,黑暗既環境下時不時顯露出些許人性光芒,但d人性光芒往往好快就熄滅,佢地背後充斥住悲劇.<br />\n<br />\n加埋d背景音樂搭配.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你係得既,fromsoftware.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/darksouls/photos/ms.c.eJxFk9mNRSEMQzsaZSFb~;42NrvMwv1ZwfAxoiOlMVoZOef~;pTxDXzqN2hW5MaF2h5pvwcU44hB4IJhI5HTZtV6jzeaTrFfTgSDSFxAQ9VOObsODaVOQ45x45Bg8XCusR9DCsjdbnsXDMsab5TLM3af0Ey~;lYKof4ZxujR6ExF9L20hrXVmxjxYlNqmys0am13~_himJAnDFgmWRBYLG8OdSTtoanWdLi8HC2IbnHhogDXZLHEESWLb0HFgnzhSunR6yEsOeBRN7ptQSp8Upm4BiGLyV4218auDa4NwE0RThRb~;D3LfbhvSy2tB49sMGenbjB9OcQh8Ih6oPWSRwsWfa9wf4M9Wlta9jGb9DDp2P4oZzCHwBdkhcs~_lv98K7sr.bps.a.1502199436519762.1073741862.119869331419453/1502199676519738/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdarksouls%2Fphotos%2Fms.c.eJxFk9mNRSEMQzsaZSFb~%3B42NrvMwv1ZwfAxoiOlMVoZOef~%3BpTxDXzqN2hW5MaF2h5pvwcU44hB4IJhI5HTZtV